Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Dairy buy-out
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xsdh
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 4 Jan 1987
Way of life ends as dairy farmers take up federal buy-out to cut excess milk production. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less